It consists of 40T data, which is comparable to the training data of chatGPT. The MNBVC dataset not only includes mainstream culture but also various niche cultures, and even data in Martian language. It encompasses pure text Chinese data in various forms such as news, compositions, novels, books, magazines, papers, dialogues, posts, wikis, ancient poems, song lyrics, product descriptions, jokes, embarrassing stories, and chat records.
